libshairport
------------------------------------------
Created by Team XBMC

This is a fork of ShairPort written by James Laird <jhl@mafipulation.org>. The
original maintainer of ShairPort had said that he intended version 0.05 to be
his last release (announcement can be found at
http://mafipulation.org/blagoblig/reversing). Therefore, the XBMC team decided
to fork ShairPort and make it into a library (libshairport) for use with XBMC.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.17-1
  libopenssl100-1.0.1e-2
  openssl-devel-1.0.1e-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-10-1
  automake-7-1
  binutils-2.22.51-2
  cygport-0.11.3-1
  gawk-4.0.1-1
  gcc4-core-4.5.3-3
  libtool-2.4-1
  make-3.82.90-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/amejia1/libshairport

Canonical download:
  git://github.com/amejia1/libshairport.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack libshairport-1.2.1+git20121215-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
         unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./libshairport-1.2.1+git20121215-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libshairport-1.2.1+git20121215-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libshairport-1.2.1+git20121215-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libshairport2-1.2.1+git20121215-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libshairport-devel-1.2.1+git20121215-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libshairport)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libshairport.README
  /usr/share/doc/libshairport/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libshairport/README

(libshairport2)
  /usr/bin/cygshairport-2.dll

(libshairport-devel)
  /usr/include/shairport/shairport.h
  /usr/lib/libshairport.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libshairport.la
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libshairport.pc

------------------

